All hidden things will be revealed by the power of the blood of Jesus.

02:21:30.280 --> 02:21:38.460
I believe with all my heart God didn't show me this stuff just to show it to me, but to tell you we have authority.

02:21:38.461 --> 02:21:43.228
And if we take our authority, we will have a victory. Do you understand?

02:21:43.229 --> 02:21:48.559
He didn't tell it to me to sit there and go, 'Well, Brandon, this is what's happening.

02:21:48.560 --> 02:21:55.072
There's nothing you can do about it.'God does not speak to hear himself talk.

02:21:55.073 --> 02:22:04.560
He speaks to make real things happen in a real world. Remember that real things happen in a real world.

02:22:04.561 --> 02:22:11.808
And He's going to show us that which is to come because His Son is coming soon.

02:22:11.809 --> 02:22:26.319
And the revival is coming. But we must expose this darkness for what it is.

02:22:26.320 --> 02:22:50.199
Glory to God. We have authority. Glory to God. It upsets you when you see kids involved in things.

02:22:50.200 --> 02:22:59.559
I have little kids of my own, and I want to know where the parents of these children I saw are.

02:22:59.560 --> 02:23:06.141
Where are these moms and dads? Why am I seeing these children going through this?

02:23:06.142 --> 02:23:14.431
There were so many of them. Where are your mom and dad? What happened to these kids?

02:23:14.432 --> 02:23:43.759
Parents, how is this happening? I don't get it. Why would you do that?

02:23:43.760 --> 02:23:53.119
Glory to God. I haven't felt the anointing lift off of me. You know, it's like Billy said, sometimes you just have to unhook.

02:23:53.120 --> 02:24:00.479
It just keeps going. I can stay on the vein for a long time. I know you're tired, son.

02:24:00.480 --> 02:24:05.639
It's like she said, 'You've just got to unhook, Brandon. You've got to unhook.'I get it.

02:24:05.640 --> 02:24:14.920
But boy, it makes me so mad when I see the stuff I've seen tonight. Do you feel like we pushed enough deep in your spirit?

02:24:14.921 --> 02:24:27.541
I mean, we could pray into that, but just what I saw in New York for hours uncovering all that stuff I saw, it just makes me...

02:24:27.542 --> 02:24:38.679
they think they're sly, and I just go, 'Father, I thank you for President Trump.

02:24:38.680 --> 02:24:45.739
You give him wisdom. Give him wisdom.'Father, visit him in the midnight hour.

02:24:45.740 --> 02:24:52.808
Give President Trump wisdom, Father, in Jesus'name. We give You all the glory, honor, and praise.

02:24:52.809 --> 02:25:10.508
Well, if you all could help me like, subscribe, click the notification bell, click the thumbs-up button, and do all that it takes to get the word out, we truly appreciate every single one of you who are helping us as you come and pray with us.

02:25:10.509 --> 02:25:14.234
I believe prayer changes things. I appreciate every single one of you.

02:25:14.235 --> 02:25:20.728
You've loved on my family so much, and you're so gracious to come here all the time and pray with us.

02:25:20.729 --> 02:25:27.951
And so I believe there's much more to uncover and there's much more to be praying about in the days ahead. It's so important.

02:25:27.952 --> 02:25:34.528
There's so much darkness that I have seen tonight, but I know that Jesus didn't show it to us so that we could just see it.

02:25:34.529 --> 02:25:44.449
It's so that we can change things. And this is to be continued for sure. There's much here.

02:25:44.450 --> 02:25:51.473
So, thank you for being a part of this and being part of this prayer night.

02:25:51.474 --> 02:25:58.525
I've got to get up early in the morning. So, I'm so thankful. Like I said, God bless you all.

02:25:58.526 --> 02:26:08.248
Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much.

